title: r/Choosingbeggars "I DESERVE ALL OF YOUR MONEY!"
description:
r/Choosingbeggars The person in today's choosing beggars post has very simple logic: his friend makes more money; therefore, he deserves all of his friends money! Makes sense, right? Well apparently it makes sense in crazy choosing beggar world, because when he doesn't get what he wants, he gets ANGRY! If you like this video and want to see more, hit the subscribe button for daily Reddit podcasts!
